# Global git excludes — applies to every repo on this machine.
#
# Git reads this automatically as the XDG default ($XDG_CONFIG_HOME/git/ignore,
# i.e. ~/.config/git/ignore) with no core.excludesfile set. Stowed from the
# `git` dotfiles package.

# Machine-local scratch files. *.local is Vite's convention (and rosetta's own
# .gitignore); we promote it to global so the pattern holds in every repo. Covers
# per-worktree scratchpad notes (notes.local.md, the Alt+m pad) and screenshots.
*.local
*.local.*

